<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<% @youngest_director = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil }).order({ :dob => :desc }) %>

<p> The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= @youngest_director.at(0).id %>"><%= @youngest_director.at(0).name %></a>, born on <%= @youngest_director.at(0).dob.strftime("%b %e, %Y") %>.
</p>
